metadata.name: Rebirth
metadata.description:
Only by experiencing the feeling of something burning inside of you do you realise that this is what people who have achieved what they have strived for have told you about.

I burn away my primal fears that have been instilled in us without our consent, and look with awe and admiration at my goal to which I am heading.

I'm burning a part of myself, a past part that stopped so long ago, that has become so heavy that it no longer wants to go on, go and explore new facets of reality.

I act as an executioner for myself, an act of self-sacrifice for a higher purpose.

I call it rebirth. 

Desinfo - 2023
